<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
	<!-- EN: Damsel in distress, kidnapped by {0} -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistressTitle>被{0}所綁架的遇險少女</CaravanDamselInDistressTitle>
	<!-- EN: We stumbled over a stunning and helpless girl held by {2} of {1}'s savages... could we bare the thought to leave her in their grasp? -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress>快看，那是{1}的旅隊！這群粗魯的野蠻人似乎抓住了一名柔弱的少女。我們要眼睜睜地看著他們把這姑娘擄走嗎？\n\n敵人數量：{2}名</CaravanDamselInDistress>
	<!-- EN: Rescue her immediately -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Rescue>馬上救下她！</CaravanDamselInDistress_Rescue>
	<!-- EN: Follow them silently until they make camp -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow>悄悄跟隨直至他們紮營休息</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow>
	<!-- EN: Leave her to her fate -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Leave>還是讓她聽天由命吧...</CaravanDamselInDistress_Leave>

	<!-- EN: You followed... -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_Title>你們悄悄地跟了上去...</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_Title>
	<!-- EN: You follow up to their camp and wait till dark, they only have 1 guard which seems rather drunk and would be easy to take. How do you proceed? -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_Main>你們悄悄跟隨在後。待到夜幕降臨時，這群野蠻人開始紮營休息了。他們唯一的守衛也喝得酩酊大醉，只需三兩下便可輕松解決。我們該怎麽做？</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_Main>
	<!-- EN: Sneak in, kill the bandits in their sleep and free the girl -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_SneakFreeGirl>隱蔽潛入，幹掉熟睡的野蠻人們並解救少女</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_SneakFreeGirl>

	<CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillSuccess_Title></CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillSuccess_Title>
	<!-- EN: You successfully cut their thoughts without them waking up and freed the surprised and hopeful looking girl. What do you want to do with her? -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillSuccess_Main>這些野蠻人已經永遠地“沈睡”下去了。被解救的少女正楚楚可憐地看著我們。我們該拿她怎麼辦？</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillSuccess_Main>
	<!-- EN: Let her be on her way, she's been through enough -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillSuccess_Free>太可憐了，放她走吧</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillSuccess_Free>
	<!-- EN: She'll make a fine slave -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KilSuccess_Slave>嘿嘿...她果然很適合做奴隸啊...</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KilSuccess_Slave>

	<!-- EN: You stepped on a twig and the guards woke up, we can either fight them or run. -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillFail_Main>*啪嚓* 有人不小心踩到了樹枝！被驚動的守衛正在叫醒他的同伴！我們要麽選擇戰鬥，要麽就此逃跑。</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillFail_Main>
	<!-- EN: Fight -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillFail_Fight>準備戰鬥！</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillFail_Fight>
	<!-- EN: Try to escape -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillFail_Leave>嘗試逃跑</CaravanDamselInDistress_Follow_KillFail_Leave>

	<!-- EN: You hear {0} asking you to come closer. -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Saved_AsksToJoin>你聽到{0}說，希望我們能再靠近點。</CaravanDamselInDistress_Saved_AsksToJoin>
	<!-- EN: Ok. -->
  <Okay>好吧。</Okay>
	<!-- EN: You hear a weak voice... -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_Saved_AsksToJoinTitle>你聽到了一個有些虛弱的聲音...</CaravanDamselInDistress_Saved_AsksToJoinTitle>

<!-- EN: {0} asks to join. -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_AsksToJoinTitle>{0}想要加入我們。</CaravanDamselInDistress_AsksToJoinTitle>
	<!-- EN: Thank you for saving my life, Would you allow me to join you on your journey? -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_AsksToJoin>感謝諸位救了我一命。但我一個人孤苦伶仃，無處可去。如果不介意的話，能讓我和你們一起走嗎？</CaravanDamselInDistress_AsksToJoin>
	<!-- EN: Yes, you're welcome to join. -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_JoinAllow>當然，歡迎你加入我們！</CaravanDamselInDistress_JoinAllow>
	<!-- EN: Sorry, we can't take the risk. -->
  <CaravanDamselInDistress_JoinDeny>很抱歉不行。我不能拿整個旅隊的安全開玩笑。</CaravanDamselInDistress_JoinDeny>
</LanguageData>